From David Garrod Subject WACO burning It is interesting sometimes to listen to news as seen through the eyes of another world news service on short wave originating out of London reports that a survivor of the Waco massacre states that a tank when making a hole in the wall of the building knocked over a kerosene lamp and that is how the fire Attempts were made by the people inside to put out the fire but it spread too Has anyone in heard anything similar or are government spin doctors censoring such information The news is also reporting that about of those that died were british